data.title: TEDxSolanaBeach
data.meta_description: TED.com, home of TED Talks, is a global initiative about ideas worth spreading via TEDx, The Audacious Project, TED Books, TED Conferences, TED-Ed and more.
data.text:
Join us for a daytime event where we explore the potential of the TEDx experience to unlock conversations about ideas that, in action, affect or may affect how we develop as a community, from local to global. Lunch included. Reserve early to personalize your experience; lunch choice, guided interactions, activities, virtual reality experience @ tedxsolanabeach.eventbrite.com. TEDxSolanaBeach is a platform for ideas that have the power to form community, to influence change in society, to improve lives, and to build beautifully.

The best information can be found at http://www.tedxsolanabeach.com.
